sequenceDiagram
    participant L as Learner
    participant WA as Web Application
    participant VL as Voice Live API
    participant CDB as Azure Cosmos DB
    participant LLM as Azure OpenAI<br/>(GPT-4.1)
    participant AVT as TTS Avatar<br/>(DragonHD)
    participant SD as Slide Display

    Note over L,SD: RUNTIME SESSION

    L->>WA: 1. Connect Avatar
    WA->>VL: 2. WebSocket + session.update<br/>{voice: DragonHD, avatar: lisa}
    VL->>AVT: 3. Avatar session config<br/>(semantic VAD, echo cancellation)
    AVT-->>WA: 4. ICE servers → WebRTC handshake
    Note over WA,AVT: WebRTC connected

    L->>WA: 5. Navigate to slide N
    WA->>CDB: 6. Fetch slide + cached translations
    WA->>SD: 7. Display slide image (SAS URL)

    Note over L,SD: TRANSLATE + SPEAK

    alt Cached translation exists in Cosmos DB
        CDB-->>WA: 8a. Return cached translated_notes
    else No cache — translate on demand
        WA->>LLM: 8b. Translate speaker notes
        LLM-->>WA: 8c. Translated text
    end

    WA->>VL: 9. conversation.item.create + response.create
    VL->>AVT: 10. TTS render (DragonHD voice)
    AVT-->>L: 11. Avatar speaks (WebRTC video+audio)
    SD-->>L: 12. Slide displayed alongside avatar

    Note over L,SD: INTERACTIVE Q&A

    L->>WA: 13. Ask question
    WA->>LLM: 14. Embed question
    WA->>WA: 15. numpy cosine search (top 3 slides)
    WA->>LLM: 16. Generate answer (RAG)
    LLM-->>WA: 17. Answer
    WA-->>L: 18. Display answer + slide refs
